  "body": "<p>Last year there was one theme that outnumbered all the rest. Extremely ornate and beautiful, any twist on Alice and Wonderland was a feast for the eyes. One that I had the pleasure of scrapbooking was \"Erika in Wonderland\". Here are just a few details from the spectacular event.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"19a-DSC_0110-600x415.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729912957-BFBWV1NGYXBDMHVVFZGN/19a-DSC_0110-600x415.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"19b-DSC_0105-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729912979-F3CECGYPLP2HQY6ZHDGK/19b-DSC_0105-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19c-DSC_0106-600x379.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729915933-K4U0X5RX38E139JMUOX4/19c-DSC_0106-600x379.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19d-wonderland-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729921907-2354QBW3N80KN833AXAZ/19d-wonderland-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19e-DSC_0111-600x434.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729922412-T0HLNTVY9427VX6FW5PG/19e-DSC_0111-600x434.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19f-DSC_0113-600x399.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729922643-9FK9DPILEUFUX2QW0H8D/19f-DSC_0113-600x399.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19g-DSC_0122-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729957666-F6JHNHZOHQFKH52MFJDN/19g-DSC_0122-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19h-DSC_0128-600x416.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729925897-H70C9AUEVKVGHO1MOWAS/19h-DSC_0128-600x416.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"19i-DSC_0130-600x396.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600729925056-7VN01XEK2Q4FVCLGS2RA/19i-DSC_0130-600x396.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>And no LA Photo Party event is complete without a few jumping photos.</p>"
